<paragraph blockId="16.[144,265,1576,1600]" box="[144,265,1576,1600]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2440">
<emphasis box="[144,265,1576,1600]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2440">Etymology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[144,1104,1615,1671]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2440">Named after the collector, J.C. Deeming, in honour of his numerous contributions to dipterology.</paragraph>
