<paragraph blockId="17.[212,330,279,303]" box="[212,330,279,303]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2441">
<emphasis box="[212,330,279,303]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2441">Comments</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[212,1172,319,439]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2441">This new species belongs to the group with reduced wing pattern, especially lacking the posterior apical band. It differs from other members of this group by the absence of a subapical tooth (remains of posterior apical band), and by the weak and strongly narrowed subapical band.</paragraph>
